title: Autodesk Mudbox 2009 (x64) - Compendium
description:
This is the 64-bit version of Mudbox 2009 only. The compendium consists of:


- Autorun enabled. You can actually burn a single file to a disc and have all of the contents intact.

- 2 different cracks (second crack is actually the cracked exe itself) with proper instructions.

- Learning movies for Mudbox 2009

- Full offline documentation (no more connecting online to read help)




Tested on Vista x64 Ultimate (SP-1) and scanned with Avast antivirus. Have fun learning (and buy the damn thing if you plan to use it for commercial reasons).
